MOOTOOLS STRETCHER

Stretches an element to fit another element. Useful for full screen backgrounds.

DEPENDENCIES

* Mootools (Tested on 1.4, should work on 1.3)

INSTALL

<div style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
	<img src="#" style="position:absolute;" id="stretchMe" />
</div>
<script>
window.addEvent('domready', function(){
	new Stretcher('stretchMe', {
		autoStretch: true
	});
});
</script>

CONFIGURE

class Stretcher(element, [options={}, setup=true]);

element		The element to stretch ()
options		Options (see below)
setup		Set to false if you plan to invoke setup() later

OPTIONS

parent(null)	Parent element
auto(false)		Stretche on load

